nethack343: nethack343 (Rogue-like game)
nethack343:
nethack343: Nethack is a single-player dungeon exploration game. The emphasis is
nethack343: on discovering the detail of the dungeon. Each game presents a
nethack343: different landscape - the random number generator provides an
nethack343: essentially unlimited number of variations of the dungeon and its
nethack343: denizens to be discovered by the player in one of a number of
nethack343: characters: you can pick your race, your role, and your gender.
